OL,3,CFast tech: Handheld fan sales take off
OL,4,Cas waste soars
OL,6,FNew research found that Brits
OL,7,Fpurchased a staggering 7.1 million
OL,8,Fmini-fans in the last year alone, ITV
OL,9,FNews Consumer Editor Chris Choi reports
OL,11,FWords by Consumer Producer Rachael
OL,12,FAllison
OL,14,FAs temperatures rise, so too does the
OL,15,FUK's obsession with handheld fans -
OL,16,Fbut experts are warning that these
OL,17,Fcooling gadgets could be harming the
OL,18,Fenvironment.
