OL,6,FNew research from Material Focus - a
OL,7,Fcharity behind the Recycle Your
OL,8,FElectricals campaign - found that
OL,9,FBrits purchased a staggering 7.1
OL,10,Fmillion mini-fans in the last year
OL,11,Falone.
OL,13,FDemand for the devices is climbing
OL,14,Ffast, with Google searches for mini-
OL,15,Ffast up 16% in May compared to the
OL,16,Fsame time last year.
OL,18,FBut what happens when the sun sets?
