OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FA staggering 3.4 million handheld fans
OL,12,Fare already sitting unused or have
OL,13,Fbeen binned - part of a wider issue
OL,14,Fknown as FastTech: small, cheap
OL,15,Felectrical items that are increasingly
OL,16,Ftreated as disposable.
OL,18,FOver a billion FastTech items are
OL,19,Fbought in the UK each year, double the
OL,20,Fnumber from 2023, with over half
OL,21,Fending up discarded.
