OL,6,FConsumer expert Professor Cathrine
OL,7,FJansson-Boyd draws comparisons to fast
OL,8,Ffashion: "FastTech is growing as
OL,9,Fquickly as fast fashion and is going
OL,10,Fto have a similar negative impact, as
OL,11,Fit ends up in landfill and has a
OL,12,Fdetrimental environmental impact."
OL,14,FBut, despite the swell in consumption
OL,15,Fhabits, there is still optimism that
OL,16,Fthe cycle can be broken by shoppers.
