OL,6,FCharlotte Blockley, a TikTok tech
OL,7,Freviewer, said: "I don't think people
OL,8,Fshould be disposing of these because
OL,9,Fyou could be using them year after
OL,10,Fyear.
OL,12,F"Some of mine I've had since 2023 -
OL,13,Fthere is no need to dispose of them
OL,14,Fafter you've used them for one summer.
OL,16,F"Just pop them in a drawer, a cupboard
OL,17,For whatever, and get them out the next
OL,18,Fsummer."
